Text:
Not sure why this torrent has a negative quality count as it in no way deserves that.

It took less than 3 minutes to download, add 30 seconds to get it running and somehow get better output quality from PPT2Video Pro than "Moyea PPT to DVD Burner Pro" that I have a paid-for-license for.

This portable version works just great. Kudos to "arulkarthik" (wtf??) : )
